releaseNotes:
1. Improved a safe whitespace minification mode;
2. `rb` and `rtc` tags are now considered as optional end tags;
3. In configuration settings of HTML minifier was added one new property - `PreservableOptionalTagList` (default is empty);
4. Fixed a error «MarkupMinificationException when having nested SVG element inside an SVG»;
5. Fixed a error «<div>${{something}}</div> incorrectly minified».
